title: Kylie Jenner raids Khloe's closet for thigh-high boots | Daily Mail Online
text: Share this article Share Jenner posed inside her Ferrari, digging the skinny heel of the boot into the luxury car's orange-red leather. Even though the young entrepreneur can surely afford her own kicks, having the Kardashians' closets at her disposal must be nice. What a lineup! Even though the young entrepreneur can surely afford her own kicks, having the Kardashians' closets at her disposal must be nice Stylish sisters: The duo both rock a pair of sexy heels on an outing in June And it's no wonder that when she wants a pair of killer heels, she would go to Khloe, 32. In 2016, Kylie's sister Kendall, 21, revealed to People : 'Khloe has the best shoe selection and she's my size.' The model also poked fun at her younger sister, saying that she's the only one that isn't generous with her abundance of designer garments. The two are notorious for fighting over clothes, and got into an especially big argument ahead of father Caitlyn Jenner's big night accepting the Arthur Ashe Courage Award at the 2015 ESPY Awards Kylie refused to let Kendall borrow a brown dress, after the model insisted she couldn't sit in the number she was wearing, suggesting that Kendall instead have her assistant pick something up from her house. However, the suggestion made the Calvin Klein model livid, with her saying: 'You're just literally the biggest f***ing b*tch I've ever met.' Then, as she goes to leave Kylie's house, she looks to her dogs and mutters: 'I'm sorry your mom is such a c***.'
